NK041(di)003:1: sa chog dpal gyi gzhi 'dzin bzhugs /
NK041(di)003:2: na mo gu ru k+shi ti gar+b+h+aa ya /
NK041(di)003:3: gang du dkyil 'khor sogs bya ba la thog mar sa brtag pa byas nas rung bar mthong na /
NK041(di)003:4: snang ba phyogs der dbang ba'i mi rnams la yon
NK041(di)003:5: sogs byin nas gnas der bslang dgos kyang rang gir
NK041(di)003:6: gyur pa'i sa phyogs su de ltar mi dgos mod
NK041(di)003:7: kyi / sngar dul ba'i sa phyogs yin yang mi
NK041(di)003:8: snang ba sa'i bdag po mi ma yin pa rnams
NK041(di)003:9: las bslang ba'i sa chog sogs mdzad srol yod pa
NK041(di)003:10: kyi / bzhin / thog mar lha gang yin gyi
NK041(di)003:11: bdag bskyed sngon du btang nas dkyil 'khor gang du
NK041(di)003:12: bya ba'i phyogs der song la /
NK041(di)003:13: lha'i nga rgyal dang ldan pas bdag gis phyogs 'dir
NK041(di)003:14: dkyil 'khor chen po bzhengs par bya'o snyam du blos
NK041(di)003:15: sa de nyid yongs su bzung ba byas te /
NK041(di)003:16: phyogs der man dal gyi dbus su dri yi thig
NK041(di)003:17: le dang me tog gi tshom bu bkod pa'i mdun
NK041(di)003:18: du nyer spyod kyi mchod pa dang /
NK041(di)003:19: dkar gtor dang dmar gtor bcas bshams /
NK041(di)003:20: mdun gyi man+dala la bkod pa'i me tog gi tshom
NK041(di)003:21: bu'i steng du pam las pad+ma dang a las zla
NK041(di)003:22: ba'i gdan la pam ser po las sa yi lha
NK041(di)003:23: mo gser gyi mdog can zhi ba'i cha lugs dang
NK041(di)003:25: phyag gnyis kyis rin po che'i bum pa thugs kar
NK041(di)003:26: bsnams pa'i 'khor du dkar po'i phyogs kyi sa bdag
NK041(di)003:27: klu gnyan thams cad kyi sa bskor ba de'i spyi
NK041(di)003:28: bor / mgrin par +aah thugs kar h'u gis mtshan
NK041(di)003:29: pa las 'od 'phros pa dang chabs gcig rang gi
NK041(di)003:30: lag g.yas sa gnon gyi phyag rgya sa la gtad
NK041(di)003:31: bor / pas / sa yi gting nas lha mo
NK041(di)003:32: 'khor dang bcas pa spyan drangs te dam tshig pa
NK041(di)003:33: la thim pas dngos su gyur /
NK041(di)003:34: mchod pa rnams la dmigs te /
NK041(di)003:36: lha rdzas las grub pa'i mchod pa'i dngos po dwangs shing thogs pa med par bsam la /
NK041(di)003:37: pri thi de w+ai sa pa ri w+aa ra ar+g+ham pra t+aits+tsha ho /
NK041(di)003:41: push+pe d+h+au pe +aa lo ke gan+d+he ni wi te shap+ta'i bar du sbyar te mchod /
NK041(di)003:42: de nas dkar gtor la dmigs te /
NK041(di)003:45: gtor ma 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga zad mi shes pa bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho chen por gyur /
NK041(di)003:46: sa yi lha mo 'khor bcas kyi ljags las 'od
NK041(di)003:47: zer byung bas gtor ma'i bcud gsol bas dgyes par
NK041(di)003:48: bsam / pri thi de w+ai sa pa ri w+aa
NK041(di)003:49: ra a k+aa ro sogs lan gsum gyis phul la
NK041(di)003:50: bsam / / mkhyen par gsol ba ni /
NK041(di)003:51: skyob pa sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK041(di)003:52: spyod pa yi ni khyad par dang //
NK041(di)003:53: sa dang pha rol phyin pa la //
NK041(di)003:54: lha mo khyod ni dpang du gyur //
NK041(di)003:55: sh+aakya seng ge skyob pa yis //
NK041(di)003:56: ji ltar bdud kyi sde bcom pa //
NK041(di)003:57: de bzhin bdag gis bdud sde las //
NK041(di)003:59: zhes lan gsum mam gcig brjod cing /
NK041(di)003:60: bdag cag rnams kyis sa phyogs 'dir //
NK041(di)003:61: lha ch+gee mo'i dkyil 'khor chen po 'bri bar 'tshal
NK041(di)003:62: na sa'i phyogs 'di bdag la gnang ba dang dngos
NK041(di)003:64: zhes brjod pas rig pa 'dzin pa khyod kyis dkyil 'khor bris shig ces gnang ba byin par bsam /
NK041(di)003:65: de nas sa'i lha mo 'khor bcas re shig gshegs
NK041(di)003:66: gsol mi bya bar dpang po'i tshul du bzhag nas
NK041(di)003:67: / sa phyogs der gnas shing rgyu ba'i 'byung po
NK041(di)003:68: gdug pa can nag po'i phyogs su gyur pa gang
NK041(di)003:69: / dag / dkyil 'khor lta ba la mi dbang ba'i bgegs kyi tshogs rnams bskrad pa ni /
NK041(di)003:71: gtor ma bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho zad pa med par gyur par dmigs la /
NK041(di)003:72: b+h+au mi pa ti sa pa ri wa ra na
NK041(di)003:73: mahsarba sogs nas kham gri h+ni dam ba lim ta
NK041(di)003:74: s+w+aa h+aa / lan gsum gyis bsngo zhing byin la /
NK041(di)003:75: dkyil 'khor chen po'i sa gzhi la gnas pa'i //
NK041(di)003:76: lha la sogs pa'i bgegs tshogs kun nyon cig /
NK041(di)003:77: ngas ni gnas 'dir dkyil 'khor chen po 'bri //
NK041(di)003:78: khyed rnams 'di nas gzhan du 'gro bar gyis //
NK041(di)003:79: gal te nga yi tshig las 'da' byed na //
NK041(di)003:80: ye shes can gyi rdo rje 'bar ba yis //
NK041(di)003:81: mgo bo tshal pa brgyar ni 'gas 'gyur zhing //
NK041(di)003:82: bgegs rnams brlag par 'gyur pa gdon mi za //
NK041(di)003:83: zhes brjod de gtor ma phyir dor zhing /
NK041(di)003:84: h'u bzhi pa'i sngags kyis rol mo'i sgra dang bcas
NK041(di)003:85: te yungs kar 'thor bas nag po'i phyogs kyi bgegs
NK041(di)003:87: de nas pri thi de w+ai sa pa ri w+aa ra badz+ra muh zhes brjod pas /
NK041(di)003:88: sa'i lha mo 'khor dang bcas pa la las sgrub
NK041(di)003:89: pa'i sdong grogs byed pas dgyes bzhin sa de nyid
NK041(di)003:91: skabs 'dir sa dbang du bya ba'i slad du phur gdab bya na /
NK041(di)003:92: slob dpon gyi lag g.yon par phur pa thogs pa /
NK041(di)003:93: g.yas pas rdo rje tho bas sa la gdab pa'am /
NK041(di)003:95: badz+ra mut+ka ra badz+ra k+ai la y+aa ko t+aa ya
NK041(di)003:96: h'u phata zhes phur pa btab pas sa dbang du
NK041(di)003:97: byas par bsam / 'di ma byas kyang chog go //
NK041(di)003:98: de nas lto 'phye tshul bzhin brtag la sa brkos te sa pra brtag par bya zhing /
NK041(di)003:99: sa yi zug rngu rnams dbyung nas slar 'thas par
NK041(di)003:100: bcag la de'i dbus su khung bu brkos te rin
NK041(di)003:101: po che sogs kyi gter sba zhing khod bsnyams la
NK041(di)003:102: / cung zad shar dang byang du gzhol ba'i dkyil
NK041(di)003:103: 'khor gyi gzhi me long gi ngos ltar dwangs ba'i
NK041(di)003:104: / skyang nur bya / de nas sbyin sreg dang
NK041(di)003:105: sngags dang phyag rgya ldan pa'i stangs stabs sna tshogs
NK041(di)003:106: kyis sa sbyangs shing mtshon cha lngas bsrung bar byas
NK041(di)003:107: / skyang nur bya / la / lha rnams kyi
NK041(di)003:108: 'od sa la bstims pas sa gzhi dkyil 'khor gyi
NK041(di)003:109: rang bzhin du bsam pas yongs su bzung ba rnams
NK041(di)003:110: rgyas par gzhan las shes par bya zhing /
NK041(di)003:111: de tsam mi dgos pa'i rigs la sa sbyang ba mdor bsdus pa ni /
NK041(di)003:112: rang gi lag mthil g.yas par yi ge h+aum bsgom
NK041(di)003:113: pa las 'od 'phros pas sa yi zug rngu sogs
NK041(di)003:114: nyes skyon thams cad bsal bar bsam la /
NK041(di)003:115: lag pas sa gzhi der chag chag bya ba'am /
NK041(di)003:117: ha na ha na kro d+ha h'u phata /
NK041(di)003:118: zhes nyer gcig gam brgya rtsa brgyad bzlas pas sbyang /
NK041(di)003:119: de nas sa gzhi de nam mkha'i rang bzhin du stong par dmigs la /
NK041(di)003:120: b+h+r+au kham zhes ci rigs brjod do //
NK041(di)003:121: de'i ngang las sa gzhi rdo rje'i rang bzhin can
NK041(di)003:122: byung ba'i steng 'og phyogs mtshams thams cad du rdo
NK041(di)003:123: rje'i ra ba dang gur la sogs pa srung ba'i
NK041(di)003:124: 'khor los yongs su gtams te bar chad gang gis
NK041(di)003:125: kyang mi tshugs pa'i rang bzhin du bsam la /
NK041(di)003:126: badz+ra rak+sha rak+sha h'u h'u h'u phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK041(di)003:128: de nas lha'i 'od kyis sa phyogs thams cad dkyil
NK041(di)003:129: 'khor gyi rang bzhin du mos pa'ang spro na bya'o
NK041(di)003:130: // de nas dkyil 'khor bzhengs pa'i sta gon du /
NK041(di)003:131: phur bu srad bu tshon phye bum pa sogs dgos pa'i yo byad thams cad 'du byas la /
NK041(di)003:132: slob dpon la dkyil 'khor bzhengs par gsol ba btab pa spro na bya /
NK041(di)003:133: rang nyid lha'i nga rgyal gyis sngags cung zad bzlas
NK041(di)003:134: nas lag pa bkrus la ba yi rnam lnga dang
NK041(di)003:135: dri bzang sbyar bas dkyil 'khor gyi gzhir lag pa
NK041(di)003:136: g.yas pas g.yon skor gyi tshul du byugs la lag
NK041(di)003:137: pa ma btegs par me tog dor bas skad cig
NK041(di)003:138: gis gzhal yas khang srung ba'i 'khor lo dang bcas
NK041(di)003:139: par bsgom / dbus su dri'i thig le gru bzhi'i
NK041(di)003:140: steng du me tog gi tshom bu bzhag ste lha
NK041(di)003:141: gang yin gyi rtsa sngags brjod pas /
NK041(di)003:142: skad cig gis dkyil 'khor gang yin gyi lha thams cad gsal btab la gnas gsum byin gyis brlabs /
NK041(di)003:144: dbang bskur zhing rigs bdag gis dbu brgyan par bsam nas /
NK041(di)003:146: chu gnyis nyer spyod dang bcas pa'i sngags sbyar te mchod /
NK041(di)003:147: badz+ra gan+de sogs kyis rol mo bya /
NK041(di)003:148: na bza' dang gtor ma 'bul zhing gsol ba gdab pa'i phyir /
NK041(di)003:149: lag pa g.yas pas rdo rje dang bcas pa'i bdug spos bzung /
NK041(di)003:151: dkyil 'khor gang yin pa de'i lha yi gtso bo la phyag 'tshal ba dang /
NK041(di)003:152: de'i dkyil 'khor 'bri ba'i kha bsgyur shes par byas la /
NK041(di)003:153: gsang ba spyi rgyud las gsungs pa'i tshig 'di brjod par bya ste /
NK041(di)003:154: 'di zhes rigs gsum mgon po bcom ldan 'das sogs kha bsgyur /
NK041(di)003:156: rig sngags rgyal la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK041(di)003:157: bdag ni brtse bar gyur nas su //
NK041(di)003:158: slob ma rnams la brtse ba dang //
NK041(di)003:159: khyed rnams la yang mchod pa'i phyir /
NK041(di)003:161: bcom ldan bdag ni gus pa la //
NK041(di)003:162: de bas gnang ba mdzad pa'i rigs //
NK041(di)003:163: sangs rgyas 'jig rten mgon brtse dang //
NK041(di)003:164: byang chub sems dpa' dgra bcom dang //
NK041(di)003:165: gsang sngags lha gzhan gang lags dang //
NK041(di)003:166: 'jig rten skyong ba'i lha rnams dang //
NK041(di)003:167: gang yang 'byung po mthu chen dang //
NK041(di)003:168: gang su lha yi spyan mnga' ba'i //
NK041(di)003:169: sems can bstan la dga' ba rnams //
NK041(di)003:170: bdag la dgongs par mdzad du gsol //
NK041(di)003:171: rig pa 'dzin pa bdag gis ni /
NK041(di)003:172: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba yis //
NK041(di)003:173: sang ni dkyil 'khor chen po'i ming //
NK041(di)003:176: sang ni 'jam dbyangs zhes bya ba'i /
NK041(di)003:177: dkyil 'khor chen po ci nus kyis /
NK041(di)003:179: 'di zhes bya ba ci nus kyis //
NK041(di)003:180: cho ga bzhin du 'bri lags na //
NK041(di)003:181: bdag dang slob mar bcas pa la //
NK041(di)003:182: thugs kyis brtse bar dgongs nas su //
NK041(di)003:183: tshogs pa thams cad dkyil 'khor du //
NK041(di)003:184: byin gyis brlab par mdzad du gsol //
NK041(di)003:185: zhes gsol ba lan gsum btab pas lha'i gnang ba byin par bsam /
NK041(di)003:186: de nas me tog la sogs pas mchod par bya'o //
NK041(di)003:187: skabs 'dir lha bum dang las bum sta gon bya na /
NK041(di)003:188: rnam rgyal bum par dkyil 'khor gyi lha dang /
NK041(di)003:189: las bum du las lha bdud rtsi 'khyil pa sogs
NK041(di)003:190: bskyed la so so'i bzlas pa bya ba sogs spyi
NK041(di)003:191: ltar bya'o // de bzhin slob ma sta gon gyi
NK041(di)003:192: cho ga dag kyang bya na gzhan las shes par
NK041(di)003:193: ltar bya'o // bya'o // mthar mchod cing bstod la ye shes pa gshegs su gsol /
NK041(di)003:194: dam tshig pa rang la bstim par bya /
NK041(di)003:195: de nas re shig dkyil 'khor gyi rdzas rnams dar sogs kyis bkab ste gzhag nas /
NK041(di)003:196: sang nang par dkyil 'khor gyi thig gdab pa dang /
NK041(di)003:197: tshon bkye ba mtshan ma 'god pa /
NK041(di)003:198: rab tu gnas shing sbyin sreg gi mthar thug pa'i mchod pa rnams ci rigs bya zhing /
NK041(di)003:199: dkyil 'khor der sgrub cing mchod pa dang /
NK041(di)003:200: slob ma rnams la dbang bskur ba sogs kyi las bya ba ya na no //
NK041(di)003:201: sa chog bsdus par sa lha'i gtor ma btang nas /
NK041(di)003:203: ha na ha na kro d+has kun rdzob tu sbyang ba dang /
NK041(di)003:204: swa b+h+aa bas don dam par sbyang ba tsam gyis chog par mdzad do //
NK041(di)003:205: de yang phyi rgyud rnams su ba byung dang dri bzang gi chag chag gdab pa dang /
NK041(di)003:206: bla med kyi dkyil 'khor rnams la bdud rtsi lnga'i
NK041(di)003:207: chag chag gdab pa sogs cho ga'i khyad par rnams
NK041(di)003:208: dang / sa cho ga kyang rgyas bsdus ci rigs mdzad pa'i phyag srol sna tshogs yod kyang /
NK041(di)003:209: 'di ni bya spyod sogs dkyil 'khor spyi yi sa
NK041(di)003:210: chog snying po bsdus pa sta gon dang bcas pa
NK041(di)003:211: yin no // tshul 'di ru dam rdzogs chen du /
NK041(di)003:212: 'dus mdo'i yan lag bya spyod dang yo ga'i sgrub
NK041(di)003:213: mchod gsar 'dzugs kyi dkyil cho ga gi sa slong
NK041(di)003:214: rang rkang ba yod na legs zhes /
NK041(di)003:215: bya spyod rigs gsum dkyil 'khor sgrub pa'i byang 'dren pa /
NK041(di)003:216: dge sbyong 'gyur med rgya mtshos nan tan bskul ngor
NK041(di)003:217: gsar rnying gi bla ma gong ma dag gi phyag
NK041(di)003:218: bzhes bzhin snying por dril te mi pham 'jam dbyangs
NK041(di)003:219: rnam rgyal zhes pas ru dam ri khrod du phral
